1
00:01:53,979 --> 00:01:54,979
Brother.

2
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:57,180
You don't understand.

3
00:01:57,180 --> 00:01:59,440
I didn't understand before, but I do now.

4
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,260
Yingluo.

5
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:04,820
I admire that about you the most.

6
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,680
We are the same kind of people.

7
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:10,660
We are both cold-hearted.

8
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:14,780
No one can warm us.

9
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:38,190
What's the silly smile for?

10
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:39,540
Your Majesty.

11
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,140
What’s this?

12
00:02:44,460 --> 00:02:46,500
Your Majesty, this is…

13
00:02:49,579 --> 00:02:50,980
I can see it from your face

14
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:54,220
that it’s from someone you like.

15
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:58,140
But this girl’s needlework

16
00:02:58,660 --> 00:03:00,060
is not good!

17
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:04,400
Your Majesty, you don't understand.

18
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:06,200
It shows her heart.

19
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:08,620
Women tend to

20
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:11,400
spend time on these small things.

21
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,780
Today she embroiders you a lotus pouch,

22
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:16,240
tomorrow a handkerchief.

23
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:18,780
Such a waste of time,

24
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:20,150
you know.

25
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:22,840
I think you should stop looking at it,

26
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,860
it won’t become a flower anyway.

27
00:03:28,340 --> 00:03:29,600
What do you want to say?

28
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:33,860
I just think

29
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:37,140
that Consort Ling has been acting differently

30
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:38,850
and she’s been rather distant to you lately.

31
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:41,850
So you're unhappy and mocking me on purpose.

32
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:45,700
Am I such a petty-minded person?

33
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:48,710
I don’t care about it at all!

34
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:50,230
She likes to be distant,

35
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:52,740
then let her be.

36
00:03:53,340 --> 00:03:55,940
We'll see how much longer I will put up with her.

37
00:03:58,020 --> 00:03:59,180
Your Majesty,

38
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:00,710
Consort Ling’s maid Mingyu

39
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:02,420
brought a hat.

40
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:05,980
Consort Ling made it personally for you.

41
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,540
See, I told you.

42
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:17,620
Women are troublesome.

43
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,380
This is?

44
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,020
Consort Ling said

45
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:34,340
a hat with this material

46
00:04:34,659 --> 00:04:36,460
is light and warm if Your Majesty

47
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:38,540
wear it in the winter.

48
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:43,980
Your Majesty, it's still hot,

49
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,600
so I'll put it away for now.

50
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:48,420
When it's winter, I'll get it back out.

51
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,540
You're just the same.

52
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:57,310
What are you saying?

53
00:04:58,260 --> 00:05:00,460
Your Majesty. I was saying

54
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:03,940
although Consort Ling seems to be cold,

55
00:05:04,140 --> 00:05:06,180
she deeply cares about you.

56
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:09,140
The fur you just sent her is sent back to you right away.

57
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:11,670
This means she's thinking of you all the time.

58
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:15,600
I didn’t ask her to do such useless thing.

59
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:18,460
When I go out, I have a bunch of people serve me.

60
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:19,660
Why would I need this?

61
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:21,280
It's unnecessary!

62
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:32,820
It's perfect.

63
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:38,380
Hu…

64
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:39,180
Ignore her!

65
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,500
She deserves it.

66
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:53,900
Hupo!

67
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:11,520
Who told you to bring her here?

68
00:06:13,380 --> 00:06:15,780
Master, she fainted on the side of the road.

69
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:17,750
She’s from the Slave House.

70
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,900
They should take her back.

71
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:24,660
When has our Palace become a shelter?

72
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,060
Take her away.

73
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,460
Sister Mingyu.

74
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:31,580
Zhenzhu,

75
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,920
if it weren't on your account,

76
00:06:34,340 --> 00:06:36,200
I wouldn't have brought her back.

77
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:37,740
Hupo.

78
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:39,390
Since you're awake now,

79
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:42,100
you should return to where you belong.

80
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,940
Your Highness Consort Ling! Your Highness Consort Ling,

81
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:45,220
I escaped!

82
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:46,620
I will be dead if I return!

83
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:48,060
I beg you, for old time’s sake…

84
00:06:48,060 --> 00:06:49,020
No,

85
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:51,100
may Your Highness be merciful

86
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,220
and spare me.

87
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:54,220
Take her away.

88
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:56,940
Your Highness Consort Ling!

89
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:57,980
I know a secret

90
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:59,340
that'll be useful to you!

91
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,020
Your Highness, please give me a chance

92
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:01,860
to make up for my mistake!

93
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:05,460
A secret that's useful to me?

94
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:08,100
Yes, if Your Highness will spare me,

95
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:10,220
I am willing

96
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:13,100
to tell you everything.

97
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:17,660
The day when the late Empress passed away,

98
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:19,260
the Madam of Duke Zhongyong…

99
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:20,860
No,

100
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:24,460
Erqing met with the late Empress.

101
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:27,780
Erqing?

102
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:29,220
Yes.

103
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:32,620
I overheard their conversation

104
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,900
when I brought tea in.

105
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,820
The mansion just received news.

106
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:41,140
And Mother fainted from crying.

107
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:42,700
I really couldn’t

108
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:45,340
bear to watch.

109
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:49,740
Tell my mother I am very well.

110
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:51,580
Don't worry.

111
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:54,940
Her eyes already have a problem.

112
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,940
Don't let her cry any more.

113
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:14,500
Erqing, what's wrong?

114
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:17,260
You’ve been bullied again?

115
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:20,750
Your Highness the Empress.

116
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:23,950
There’s a secret I’ve been hidden for so long.

117
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:26,580
I didn't dare to mention to anyone.

118
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:30,400
I wanted to repent to Mother at first.

119
00:08:30,660 --> 00:08:32,020
But the Seventh Prince…

120
00:08:34,539 --> 00:08:36,419
I saw how sad Mother was.

121
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:41,720
So I didn’t dare to make the situation worse.

122
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,820
What has happened exactly?

123
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,060
That night.

124
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:54,750
That night was Second Prince's memorial.

125
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:58,680
His Majesty stayed at Palace of Eternal Spring.

126
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:01,420
I was angry at Fuheng

127
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:03,350
and he wouldn't even listen to you.

128
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:05,100
So I thought,

129
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,990
this marriage was granted by His Majesty.

130
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,670
As long as His Majesty talks to him,

131
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:13,300
Fuheng will treat me nicer.

132
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:15,980
So,

133
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,980
I entered the side chamber.

134
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:25,980
Who knew

135
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:34,980
that His Majesty was drunk and insisted on favoring me.

136
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,980
I couldn't dare to object.

137
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:40,740
I was afraid someone would come in,

138
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:42,700
and ruin Fuca's reputation.

139
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:47,060
But later I found out that

140
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:51,980
I am pregnant!

141
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:55,980
What did you say?

142
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:59,540
I am pregnant.

143
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:17,620
Bitch! Bitch!

144
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:24,340
Your Highness, as long as you say the word,

145
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,940
I’m willing to die

146
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:29,180
to protect Fuca’s reputation!

147
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:31,100
Reputation?

148
00:10:33,060 --> 00:10:34,180
The Fucas

149
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:37,860
have no reputation anymore!

150
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:43,180
It’s you!

151
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:48,020
It’s all your fault!

152
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:53,460
I never want to see you ever again!

153
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:58,020
Your Highness, I deserve to die,

154
00:10:58,820 --> 00:11:00,140
but this trouble

155
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:02,260
was started by His Majesty.

156
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:07,940
You are all

157
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:15,700
the closest people to me.

158
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:21,020
Why did you join hands

159
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:26,420
to treat me like this?

160
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:29,860
Why?

161
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:42,680
I will go and apologize to Mother now.

162
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,580
I will let her punish me!

163
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,060
Stop!

164
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:54,060
What you

165
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:57,420
told me today

166
00:12:00,820 --> 00:12:02,620
shall not be told

167
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:06,300
to mother!

168
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:10,900
You

169
00:12:13,180 --> 00:12:14,180
are never allowed

170
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:17,420
to enter the palace again!

171
00:12:19,820 --> 00:12:21,180
Ever!

172
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,280
Are you telling the truth?

173
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:42,500
I can swear to God that every word is true.

174
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:45,300
Do you remember that morning

175
00:12:46,060 --> 00:12:49,500
you saw me clean up the side chamber?

176
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:54,020
Hupo.

177
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:56,120
What are you doing?

178
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:58,060
Sister Mingyu.

179
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:03,040
Last night, His Majesty was drunk and vomited everywhere.

180
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:06,550
So that undergarment was hers.

181
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:09,550
Can’t believe, she…

182
00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:13,180
When I first entered the palace,

183
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:14,840
I was cared for by Erqing a lot.

184
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:18,060
She at first told me she had an urgent matter

185
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:19,460
to tell His Majesty.

186
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:21,620
I was soft-hearted and let her.

187
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:24,390
I didn’t think such thing would’ve happened.

188
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:25,780
I was so scared.

189
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:28,600
I didn't dare to mention it to anyone.

190
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:30,460
Your Highness Consort Ling,

191
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:32,620
please spare me on the account that

192
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:34,040
I told you this secret!

193
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:36,220
Servants!

194
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:41,340
Your Highness!

195
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:43,340
Take her away and lock her up for now.

196
00:13:44,660 --> 00:13:46,020
Without my order,

197
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,540
don't let her meet anyone.

198
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:49,100
Yes.

199
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:51,940
Your Highness, you agreed to spare me.

200
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,820
Your Highness, you’ve got to keep your word!

201
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:54,820
I don’t want to return to

202
00:13:54,820 --> 00:13:56,580
the Slave House again!

203
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:58,310
Your Highness! Your Highness!

204
00:13:58,500 --> 00:14:00,900
You agreed to spare me! Your Highness!

205
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:02,180
Your Highness!

206
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:17,020
Yingluo, someone like her

207
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:19,670
deserves to be hacked into mincemeat!

208
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:26,980
The true cause of the disaster

209
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,500
It's Hitara Erqing

210
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:47,220
I greet Your Highness Consort Ling.

211
00:14:50,940 --> 00:14:53,820
Today, His Majesty summoned the military commanders to a discussion.

212
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:55,140
He won't be able to come himself,

213
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:58,540
so he had me bring you some delicious dishes.

214
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:05,700
Wild duck with butter.

215
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:08,300
Four small appetizers.

216
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:12,300
Swallow's nest with shredded chicken.

217
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:13,540
Polished rice.

218
00:15:22,100 --> 00:15:23,020
Your Highness,

219
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:24,220
His Majesty also send you

220
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:26,220
that Chef Zhang from Suzhou

221
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:27,860
you once praised.

222
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:30,100
He will cook for you in the future.

223
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:39,320
I thank His Majesty for the grace.

224
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:48,920
Since the chef and the dishes are delivered,

225
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:51,030
you can leave now, chamberlain Li.

226
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:52,980
Yes.

227
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:02,300
Yingluo.

228
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:13,780
What’s that sound?

229
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:16,750
I didn’t hear anything!

230
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:24,470
Take care, Chamberlain Li.

231
00:16:28,820 --> 00:16:30,100
Be careful!

232
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:31,830
Take them all to Silkworm Hall!

233
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:32,820
Be careful.

234
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:33,960
That's a gold hook!

235
00:16:35,180 --> 00:16:37,300
Hurry up! Don't miss the auspicious time.

236
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:38,100
Hurry!

237
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:46,580
Your Majesty, the Silkworm Ceremony is ready.

238
00:16:48,140 --> 00:16:50,620
Tell the Empress I will be there soon.

239
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:52,220
Yes.

240
00:16:53,340 --> 00:16:54,180
Well…

241
00:16:57,220 --> 00:16:58,020
What's wrong?

242
00:17:00,900 --> 00:17:02,960
Duchess Zhongyong begs an audience.

243
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:36,700
Fuheng favored a handmaiden,

244
00:17:37,260 --> 00:17:38,860
causing a huge chaos at home.

245
00:17:39,780 --> 00:17:42,300
That handmaiden talked slanderously about me

246
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:45,360
and even made Fuheng suspect if An’er is really his son.

247
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:46,620
I was so angry

248
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:48,300
that I married her off!

249
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:51,030
Then Fuheng threatened to divorce me.

250
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:52,900
But how could it possible?!

251
00:17:53,260 --> 00:17:55,220
This marriage was granted by Your Majesty.

252
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:56,880
He of course can’t divorce me.

253
00:17:57,060 --> 00:17:58,520
Mother wouldn't allow it.

254
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:01,340
Fuheng took his anger out on me.

255
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:04,670
He confined me to the Buddhist shrine.

256
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:07,500
Mother is ill and in bed.

257
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,020
Fuheng just ignores her.

258
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,790
Because of the Silkworm Ceremony,

259
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:15,670
I finally got a chance to get out

260
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:17,980
to beg Your Majesty.

261
00:18:25,220 --> 00:18:26,060
Erqing.

262
00:18:29,540 --> 00:18:30,540
Tell me.

263
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,820
Is An’er really…

264
00:18:40,820 --> 00:18:42,220
Though

265
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:46,820
I sinned before,

266
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:49,620
it’s all in the past.

267
00:18:51,020 --> 00:18:52,500
I wanted to be a good daughter-in-law

268
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:54,030
of Fuca with all sincerity.

269
00:18:55,020 --> 00:18:56,820
Fuheng fights in battles all along,

270
00:18:56,820 --> 00:18:57,580
I'm always the one

271
00:18:57,580 --> 00:18:59,460
taking care of the housework

272
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:00,990
and caring for the parents.

273
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:02,900
I never made any mistake.

274
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:04,700
Your Majesty,

275
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:07,340
I can swear.

276
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:11,940
Fu Kang'an is Fuheng's son.

277
00:19:12,260 --> 00:19:13,900
He is a child of the Fucas.

278
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:16,780
But no matter how I explain,

279
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,880
Fuheng just won't believe it.

280
00:19:19,540 --> 00:19:21,340
Fuheng forced my son and I to part,

281
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:22,800
a pain harsher than death.

282
00:19:23,460 --> 00:19:24,380
Your Majesty,

283
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:26,220
I know

284
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:29,060
Your Majesty doesn’t usually care about the subject's family affair.

285
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:31,660
But this marriage was granted by Your Majesty.

