Take some people

566
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:22,740
to clean up the body of the wife of Duke Zhongyong.

567
00:36:23,780 --> 00:36:25,140
Don't leave any signs.

568
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:28,700
Just tell the others that she was suddenly summoned by Empress Dowager

569
00:36:28,700 --> 00:36:29,900
and said a few words.

570
00:36:30,660 --> 00:36:32,580
Then she rushed out of the celebration,

571
00:36:32,580 --> 00:36:34,820
realizing that she missed the auspicious time.

572
00:36:34,820 --> 00:36:36,220
After everyone had left,

573
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:38,980
a small sedan took her back to the Fuca mansion.

574
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:41,300
She was struck with a disease on the way.

575
00:36:41,580 --> 00:36:44,640
Embargo the news. Issue the obituary seven days later.

576
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:48,340
But I need Fuca Mansion to cooperate with us.

577
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:50,540
I’ll send someone

578
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:52,580
to persuade Old Madam Fuca.

579
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:54,900
As for Consort Ling,

580
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:57,580
we’ll tell people…

581
00:36:59,780 --> 00:37:01,020
That she is sick!

582
00:37:06,580 --> 00:37:07,660
Your Majesty,

583
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:10,420
Am I sick?

584
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:11,220
You are!

585
00:37:12,500 --> 00:37:13,700
Quite serious too!

586
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:16,380
So,

587
00:37:17,740 --> 00:37:19,420
just go back to your palace

588
00:37:19,900 --> 00:37:22,580
and summon the Imperial Doctor to treat you!

589
00:37:24,020 --> 00:37:25,680
I will comply with your order.

590
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:54,180
Consort Ling, you were too reckless.

591
00:37:54,340 --> 00:37:57,200
She was the wife of Duke Zhongyong of the First Rank.

592
00:37:57,380 --> 00:37:58,900
How could you kill her

593
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:01,220
without even asking His Majesty?

594
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:09,700
Hitara Erqing was His Majesty's lover.

595
00:38:11,260 --> 00:38:13,190
Would His Majesty bear to kill her?

596
00:38:14,220 --> 00:38:15,900
In terms of your decisiveness to kill,

597
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:17,380
I do admire you.

598
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:20,420
It's a pity that just because of

599
00:38:20,900 --> 00:38:22,300
Hitara Erqing,

600
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:25,140
you will lose His Majesty’s favor.

601
00:38:25,140 --> 00:38:26,420
Is it worth it?

602
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:29,750
When I mentioned

603
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:33,900
that Hitara Erqing was His Majesty’s lover,

604
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:39,380
Your Highness was not surprised at all.

605
00:38:40,580 --> 00:38:42,180
Did you know that already?

606
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:46,700
Even if you know,

607
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:49,100
you should pretend that you don’t know.

608
00:38:49,180 --> 00:38:51,420
That’s how you live a longer life in the palace.

609
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:54,550
That’s how you can be the last one standing and laughing.

610
00:38:58,220 --> 00:39:01,300
Consort Ling, you must remember

611
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:03,340
my warning to you today.

612
00:39:03,860 --> 00:39:04,900
So, it was you.

613
00:39:05,900 --> 00:39:07,430
What are you talking about?

614
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:13,660
The one who sent Hupo to me

615
00:39:15,980 --> 00:39:16,900
was you!

616
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:25,060
I don't understand what you are saying.

617
00:39:26,980 --> 00:39:29,580
Before Hupo told me,

618
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:32,420
I believe that

619
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,820
you’d already heard the truth

620
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:36,980
from her.

621
00:39:39,380 --> 00:39:43,620
Thus, you deliberately sent Erqing to me

622
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:46,590
and you were certain

623
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:49,060
that I must kill Erqing.

624
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:52,580
Empress,

625
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:57,100
I’m impressed by

626
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:02,340
your trick of killing someone with a borrowed knife.

627
00:40:02,340 --> 00:40:03,580
Whose knife did I borrow?

628
00:40:03,580 --> 00:40:04,620
Mine!

629
00:40:08,140 --> 00:40:09,340
Who was killed?

630
00:40:09,620 --> 00:40:11,580
Hitara Erqing.

631
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:18,260
And you also took away His Majesty’s favor from me.

632
00:40:20,620 --> 00:40:23,420
His Majesty said that you are sick. I didn't believe it.

633
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:26,460
But now I see that you are really sick!

634
00:40:27,500 --> 00:40:29,180
Go back and rest.

635
00:40:43,140 --> 00:40:44,020
Yingluo.

636
00:40:45,940 --> 00:40:47,340
Did we fall into her trap?

637
00:40:49,580 --> 00:40:50,860
Mingyu.

638
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:55,020
Do you regret

639
00:40:57,380 --> 00:40:59,240
that you killed Erqing in person?

640
00:41:01,660 --> 00:41:02,580
No.

641
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:04,900
I don’t!

642
00:41:06,660 --> 00:41:08,180
She deserved it!

643
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:13,660
That’s why the Empress has outsmarted us.

644
00:41:16,500 --> 00:41:18,780
She figured out every step we’d go,

645
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:22,460
having us willingly

646
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:25,220
fall into her trap.

647
00:41:31,180 --> 00:41:32,140
Your Majesty,

648
00:41:32,820 --> 00:41:34,820
it's past the meal hour.

649
00:42:04,220 --> 00:42:05,260
Your Majesty.

650
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:12,140
What are you doing here?

651
00:42:12,140 --> 00:42:13,340
I…

652
00:42:15,660 --> 00:42:17,340
Since I left the palace,

653
00:42:18,500 --> 00:42:20,060
I’ve suffered a lot from

654
00:42:21,620 --> 00:42:23,750
Fuheng’s coldness and indifference.

655
00:42:24,340 --> 00:42:27,380
I wanted to talk to the Empress and find some comfort.

656
00:42:27,740 --> 00:42:29,980
But Her Highness is pregnant,

657
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:32,220
so I dared not disturb her.

658
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:34,740
I thus came to Your Majesty to seek help.

659
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:37,980
But,

660
00:42:40,420 --> 00:42:42,820
Your Majesty was drunk last night.

661
00:42:43,700 --> 00:42:45,540
I know I’ve sinned.

662
00:42:46,460 --> 00:42:48,460
I’m willing to die for my sin.

663
00:42:49,420 --> 00:42:51,140
But Your Majesty, I beg you.

664
00:42:51,860 --> 00:42:53,300
I beg Your Majesty

665
00:42:53,580 --> 00:42:55,380
to spare my family.

666
00:42:57,020 --> 00:43:02,420
I'm willing to be a slave to repay Your Majesty's grace in the next life.

667
00:43:09,740 --> 00:43:11,580
If you died here at Palace of Eternal Spring,

668
00:43:11,580 --> 00:43:13,580
you would be insulting the Empress!

669
00:43:14,980 --> 00:43:15,740
Your Majesty!

670
00:43:15,740 --> 00:43:16,780
Get out!

671
00:43:38,980 --> 00:43:41,740
I heard the best items were sent to Palace of Everlasting Joy.

672
00:43:41,740 --> 00:43:43,200
His Majesty is too biased.

673
00:43:43,540 --> 00:43:46,500
Just some insignificant stuff after all.

674
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:49,320
This represents His Majesty's grace

675
00:43:49,420 --> 00:43:51,020
and the dignity of the harem.

676
00:43:51,860 --> 00:43:54,860
Before, the best fur from Kyakhta

677
00:43:55,260 --> 00:43:57,300
were all sent to our palace

678
00:43:57,500 --> 00:43:59,140
and distributed by Your Highness.

679
00:43:59,140 --> 00:44:00,340
But now it’s changed.

680
00:44:01,660 --> 00:44:04,860
However, Consort Ling killed the wife of Duke Zhongyong.

681
00:44:05,180 --> 00:44:07,240
She seriously offended His Majesty.

682
00:44:07,700 --> 00:44:10,140
Would she completely lose favor from now on?
